      				<h3>Locations</h3>
              <p>You want to go play a pick up game of baseball? You have a big date to plan? You want to get together with some old friends from college for drinks? You want to invite your family over your house for the holidays? One thing these all have in common is how hard it is to invite everyone and get confirmation of who's going at short or long term notice.  Now with Let's Hang, let everyone you want to invite know where to go, when to go and you will see who's coming and who can't make it.  Any last minute changes to the event? No worries, Let's Hang will notify the people you invite of these changes in real time.</p>
      			</div>
