              <p>Things up in the air and want to talk it over with friends? Thanks to Let's Hang's built in messaging system, you have real time communication with all those invited to an event.</p>
      			</div>
      			<div class="col-md-4">
      				<h3>Privacy</h3>
              <p>Don't worry, not everyone will see your event.  Only those you invite to the event can see the event.  You're able to pick and choose your contacts from all major social media platforms, and you can add or delete those who see you're using Let's Hang.  When you delete a contact, they're deleted for good unless you choose to add them again.  Any private data is encrypted and the only emails you will recieve from us are event notifications, account management emails (i.e. forgot password), and news on major updates to Let's Hang.</p>
